Following this, Ori improved our GitHub board, which has significantly streamlined my workflow.\\\\n- Engaged in several discussions with the team to explore enhancements to the\\\\u{a0}**Proposal Portal**, aiming to maximize its usability and effectiveness.\\\\n\\\\n#### Completed Tasks\\\\n\\\\n- **Add \\\\\\\"Refresh\\\\\\\" Data Button**\\\\u{a0}[#87](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-treasury-dashboard/issues/87)\\\\n- **Governance Setting UI (Threshold & Vote Duration)**\\\\u{a0}[#86](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-treasury-dashboard/issues/86)\\\\n- **Improve Voting Options & Horizontal Scroll**\\\\u{a0}[#79](https://github.com/NEAR-DevHub/neardevhub-treasury-dashboard/issues/79)\\\\n\\\\n#### **Cost**\\\\n\\\\n- **Rate**: $2,500/month\\\\n- **Total Amount**: $2,500 USD", "linked_proposals": [224], "receiver_account": "freski.near", "requested_sponsor": "neardevdao.near", "proposal_body_version": "V0", "requested_sponsorship_usd_amount": "2500", "requested_sponsorship_paid_in_currency": "USDT"}, "labels": []}
